 (1,'Novotel Ambassador Seoul Dongdaemun','238, Eulji-ro, Jung-gu, Seoul 04561 South Korea','With a premium central Seoul location and an incredible view of cityscape, the hotel is situated adjacent to the famous Dongdaemun Design Plaza and Dongdaemun Market.The hotel will offer an unforgettable experience for both business and leisure travelers. It boasts 331 guest rooms and 192 residences with a stunning rooftop bar and the outdoor infinity pool. ','4.5','52/684','372','https://dynamic-media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/17/a4/73/d4/exterior-view.jpg?w=200&h=200&s=1','114.000 krw','Seoul','South Korea','Hotel','kr'),
 (2,'Banyan Tree Club & Spa Seoul','60, Jangchungdan-ro, Jung-gu, Seoul 04605 South Korea','Banyan Tree Club & Spa Seoul is the first urban resort of awards-winning Banyan Tree Hotel & Resort. Banyan Tree on the land of 70,000 square meters is located in NamSan at the center of Seoul and you can enjoy sound resting and private time away from daily life.','4.5','86/684','653','https://dynamic-media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/1b/45/28/57/exterior.jpg?w=400&h=300&s=1','310.675 krw','Seoul','South Korea','Hotel','kr'),
 (3,'Park Hyatt Seoul','606 Teheran-ro, Gangnam-gu, Seoul 06174 South Korea','In response to COVID-19, we are taking multiple steps to care for your wellbeing. Precautionary measures include enhanced cleaning and sanitization procedures in all guestrooms, dining outlets and public spaces in an effort to maintain a safe environment for you and your loved ones. ___ See why so many travelers make Park Hyatt Seoul their hotel of choice when visiting Seoul. Providing an ideal mix of value, comfort and convenience, it offers a luxury setting with an array of amenities designed for travelers like you. While staying at Hyatt Seoul, visitors can check out Jamsil Sports Complex (0.5 mi) and Seolleung & Jeongneung Royal Tomb (1.0 mi), some of Seoul\'s top attractions. Rooms at Park Hyatt Seoul Hotel provide a flat screen TV, air conditioning, and a minibar, and guests can stay connected with free wifi. In addition, while staying at Seoul Hyatt guests have access to a 24 hour front desk, room service, and a concierge. You can also enjoy a pool and a lounge. Need a place to park? Parking is available at Park Hyatt Seoul Hotel. When you’re feeling hungry, be sure to check out Il Piatto, Ithaca, and Sobremesa, which are some Mediterranean restaurants that are popular with locals and out-of-towners alike. During your visit, be sure to check out Bongeunsa Temple (0.6 mi), which is a popular attraction within walking distance of the hotel. At Park Hyatt Seoul, your comfort and satisfaction come first, and they look forward to welcoming you to Seoul.','4.5','66/684','1646','https://dynamic-media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/1a/98/66/5b/exterior.jpg?w=300&h=300&s=1','345.000 krw','Seoul','South Korea','Hotel','kr'),
 (4,'Four Seasons Hotel Seoul','97 Saemunan-ro, Jongno-gu, Seoul 03183 South Korea','Relax in the South Korean capital’s largest luxury hotel accommodations. Four Seasons Hotel Seoul offers 317 spacious guest rooms, including 43 suites – all with high-tech convenience, spa-like bathrooms and customizable Four Seasons beds. Floor-to-ceiling windows flood the interiors with natural light, while highlighting impressive views of the cityscape.','4.5','10/684','1756','https://dynamic-media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/1b/45/35/af/exterior.jpg?w=400&h=300&s=1','345.000 krw','Seoul','South Korea','Hotel','kr'),
 (5,'Grand Mercure Ambassador Hotel and Residences Seoul Yongsan','95, Cheongpa-ro 20-gil, Yongsan-gu, Seoul 04372 South Korea','Grand Mercure Ambassador Hotel and Residences Seoul Yongsan is a high-end hotel where tradition harmoniously blends with modernity. AccorHotels’ luxury serviced residence brand Grand Mercure opens its first doors in Korea, in the very heart of Seoul—where old palaces and skyscrapers make up a striking cityscape together. Experience first-class hospitality at Grand Mercure Ambassador Hotel and Residences Seoul Yongsan. The hotel has 202 guest rooms providing fantastic night views of Seoul, each with up to three bedrooms, a full kitchen and a variety of household items. Guests can also savor the world’s best delicacies at hotel restaurants, relax in the Executive Floor Lounge, or work out in the indoor golf room or fitness center. Grand Mercure Ambassador Hotel and Residences Seoul Yongsan, where top-class hospitality is combined with cultural stories, is the ideal place to feel and discover more about Korea.','5.0','7/684','356','https://dynamic-media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/18/87/ea/8b/exterior-view.jpg?w=400&h=300&s=1','253.250 krw','Seoul','South Korea','Hotel','kr'),
 (6,'Grand Hyatt Seoul Hotel','322 Sowol-ro, Yongsan-gu, Seoul 04347 South Korea','This Seoul hotel is the ideal place to discover the vibrant culture and beauty of South Korea. Our recently renovated rooms and suites invoke a new standard of luxury coupled with the unparalleled convenience of being just minutes from downtown Seoul, Myeongdong and Itaewon. This spectacular urban retreat is a perfect destination for corporate travel, family vacations or conference gatherings with the Han River and Mount Namsan as your backdrop, making every moment extraordinary.','4.0','104/684','411','https://dynamic-media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/19/57/d0/02/exterior.jpg?w=400&h=300&s=1','234.500 krw','Seoul','South Korea','Hotel','kr'),
 (7,'Vista Walkerhill Seoul','177, Walkerhill-ro, Gwangjin-gu, Seoul 04963 South Korea','Experience the ultimate in relaxation with unparalleled value, including comfortable and stylish interiors with natural surroundings. SUSTAINABLE LUXURY Resting cloudlike on the slopes of Achasan Maountain overlooking Hangang River, Vista Walkerhill Seoul is an enchanting urban resort that offers incomparable natural beauty. Advanced technology allows our guests to enjoy future-like experience while surrounded by nature. Creating a space where people, nature and the future coexist, the Vista Walkerhill Seoul is leader in providing a creative lifestyle and cultural experience with an emphasis on providing sustainable luxury.','4.5','18/684','549','https://dynamic-media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/0f/4a/d7/3b/vista-walkerhill-seoul.jpg?w=400&h=300&s=1','231.000 krw','Seoul','South Korea','Hotel','kr'),
 (8,'Lotte Hotel Seoul Executive Tower','30, Eulji-ro, Jung-gu Lotte Hotel Seoul, Seoul 04533 South Korea','Ideally placed at the center of dynamic Seoul, Lotte Hotel Seoul Executive Tower offers unparalleled elegance and sophistication within walking distance of the city\'s central business and shopping districts. Tucked into a sleek corner of Seoul, Lotte Hotel Seoul Executive Tower is a luxurious destination catering to business and leisure travelers alike. This newly renovated section of the hotel offers the utmost sophistication and luxury, along with detailed and exclusive VIP services. From high-end venues for family gatherings, luxury weddings and large-scale business events to a tempting variety of international cuisines, guests have endless options at their fingertips.','5.0','1/684','155','https://dynamic-media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/1b/59/b2/40/caption.jpg?w=300&h=-1&s=1','315.000 krw','Seoul','South Korea','Hotel','kr'),
 (9,'Conrad Seoul','10, Gukjegeumyung-ro, Yeongdeungpo-gu, Seoul 07326 South Korea','Conrad Seoul is located in the acclaimed International Finance Centre (IFC) in Seoul’s Yeouido Business District.In addition to its prime location in what is often referred as the ‘Korean Wall Street, Conrad Seoul is the closest luxury hotel to both Incheon and Gimpo International Airports. It affords easy access to two subway lines and a bus terminal with connections to every part of the city and environs. Dramatically overlooking the Han River, and with sweeping views of the city skyline, Conrad Seoul is nestled among three other high-profile office towers of the IFC, a complex which includes a Cineplex, a luxury retail mall, and extensive dining and leisure outlets. For business, for pleasure, for entertaining, or for just relaxing with friends, Conrad Seoul truly is the center of it all.','4.5','71/684','2485','https://dynamic-media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/19/dd/8e/af/exterior.jpg?w=400&h=300&s=1','300.000 krw','Seoul','South Korea','Hotel','kr'),
 (10,'JW Marriott Hotel Seoul','176, Sinbanpo-ro, Seocho-gu, Seoul 06546 South Korea  ','Set your sights on unparalleled luxury here at JW Marriott Hotel Seoul. With a perfect location in Central City, Seoul, South Korea, an extensive multi-purpose complex, we provide the backdrop for truly memorable visits. Gorgeous rooms and suites at our Gangnam hotel are filled with luxury perks - from high-speed Internet access and flat-screen TVs to marble bathrooms and plush bedding. Many showcase terrific views of the Seoul city skyline or the river. Start your morning with a workout in our three-floor gym, or a dip in the indoor pool. Our hotel also offers a luxury spa, so you can pamper yourself during your visit. Delicious on-site dining options include a steakhouse and a Japanese eatery with a sushi bar. Those hosting events in Seoul will be thrilled with our flexible venues, which offer natural light and audiovisual facilities. And thanks to our convenient location, you\'re just steps away from shopping at Shinsegae Department Store, Famille Street, and much more. Visit us at JW Marriott Hotel Seoul!','5.0','9/684','461','https://dynamic-media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/1b/6c/a2/d9/exterior.jpg?w=400&h=300&s=1','270.000 krw','Seoul','South Korea','Hotel','kr'),
 (11,'Andaz Seoul Gangnam','854, Nonhyeon-ro, Gangnam-gu, Seoul 06022 South Korea','Andaz Seoul Gangnam is conveniently located in the heart of Seoul Gangnam area with direct access to Apgujeong metro station. The hotel is nearby from affluent Cheongdam and Apgujeong neighborhoods where you can explore Korean Chic with luxury fashion and beauty, art museums and culinary delights. Andaz Seoul Gangnam houses 241 comfortable, contemporary, unique rooms in soothing shades of Turkish blue and ochre by award-winning Dutch designers Studio Piet Boon. The hotel’s 25 suites offer a separate living room, while the Gangnam Penthouse on the highest floor is an imaginative space for entertaining featuring an additional vast terrace, bar, kitchen, dining area for 20 and TV','4.5','137/684','154','https://dynamic-media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/1a/02/ff/84/andaz-seoul-gangnam-exterior.jpg?w=400&h=300&s=1','283.500 krw','Seoul','South Korea','Hotel','kr'),
 (12,'Sheraton Seoul Palace Gangnam Hotel','160, Sapyeong-daero, Seocho-gu, Seoul 06578 South Korea','Experience exquisite and world-class service only fit for Sheraton\'s reputation at Sheraton Seoul Palace Gangnam (previously The Palace Hotel Seoul) at the heart of cultural trends and business districts. Sheraton Seoul Palace Gangnam is located near government offices such as courts and prosecutor\'s offices, international convention centers including COEX and SETEC, Seoul Arts Center, Central City, Seoul St. Mary\'s Hospital, and more. It offers guests a quality, cultural experience and safe retreat. With subway lines 3, 7, and 9 nearby, which connect to key tourist sites throughout Seoul, and a nationwide bus terminal just five minutes away, guests have easy access to business, shopping, touring, and leisure. With its convenient location, Sheraton Seoul Palace Gangnam is ideal for holding small business meetings, seminars, weddings and conferences with nine different banquet halls including two grand ballrooms. Visitors can recharge in the hotel\'s 341 rooms including 22 suites, Club Lounge, fitness center with advanced equipment, indoor swimming pool with an expansive view, world-class spa, and other renovated facilities. The hotel offers the finest cuisine with four restaurants including famous Japanese restaurant \"TA BONG\" and Chinese restaurant \"SUH GOONG\" in addition to nearby restaurants and trendy tourist spots such as Seorae Village, Itaewon, and Garosugil. As Gangnam\'s first luxury hotel, Sheraton Seoul Palace Gangnam provides a special experience that you will remember through its innovative and detailed service with a systematic expertise that belongs to Sheraton\'s brand and long history.','4.0','151/684','710','https://dynamic-media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/0b/c0/1d/8e/the-palace-hotel-seoul.jpg?w=400&h=300&s=1','180.000 krw','Seoul','South Korea','Hotel','kr'),
 (13,'Hotel Entra Gangnam','508, Dosan-daero, Gangnam-gu, Seoul 06070 South Korea','Situated in the mecca of high fashion and fine dining, the Hotel ENTRA is located at Cheongdam Crossroad in Gangnam-gu, surrounded by boundless access to an array of activities and shopping areas such as the Cheongdam Fashion Streets,street of Garosu-gil, the COEX mall, and various K-Pop Entertainment headquarters.','4.0','192/684','106','https://dynamic-media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/0e/92/51/f1/hotel-entra-gangnam.jpg?w=400&h=300&s=1','110.000 krw','Seoul','South Korea','Hotel','kr'),
 (14,'The Westin Chosun Seoul','106 Sogong-Ro, Jung-Gu, Seoul 04533 South Korea','Situated in the heart of Seoul\'s main business and shopping district, the Westin Chosun Seoul is within easy walking distance of major embassies, banks, commercial and government offices, as well as national museums, historic palaces and local markets. 462 Spacious rooms, including 40suites, are exceptionally furnished with every modern amenity. Advanced features include Westin\'s signature Heavenly Bed, anti-allergy carpet, premium espresso coffee machine, LED TV with Internet, oversized beds, individually controlled air-conditioning, refrigerator, mini bar, in-room electronic safe, full-size writing desk with office task chair, and voice mail. • Institutional Investor - World\'s Top 100 Hotels (4 consecutive years) • Asiamoney - Best Hotel in Seoul (3 consecutive years) • Travel +Leisure - World\'s Best 500 Hotels • Conde Nast Travel - Best Hotel in Seoul • Smart Travel Asia - Asia\' Top 25 Business Hotels (5 consecutive years)','4.5','72/684','2963','https://dynamic-media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/06/e1/ef/b4/caption.jpg?w=400&h=300&s=1','255.000 krw','Seoul','South Korea','Hotel','kr'),
 (15,'Nine Tree Premier Hotel Insadong','49, Insadong-gil, Jongno-gu, Seoul 03145 South Korea','NINE TREE PREMIER HOTEL INSADONG is the third branch of Nine Tree Hotel, the business brand of Parnas Hotel Co., Ltd. specialized in hotel businesses. It is located in the best spot for convenient visits to Gyeongbokgung, Insa-dong, Gwanghwamun, and Cheonggyecheon Stream, representing the beauty of Korea. Located in Insadong full of Korean tastes and relaxations in the dynamic daily life of a splendid city, Nine Tree Hotel provides good rest and Korean traditional stylishness. It includes 301 super delux first class guestrooms and 4 meeting rooms as well as the all-day dining restaurant, Loungy 9, and rooftop garden.','4.0','233/684','20','https://dynamic-media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/19/5e/37/a4/caption.jpg?w=400&h=300&s=1','326.227 krw','Seoul','South Korea','Hotel','kr'),
 (16,'The Plaza Seoul','119, Sogong-ro, Jung-gu, Seoul 04525 South Korea','THE PLAZA Seoul, AutographCollection, the newly renovated hotel features aesthetic interior designs, impeccable personalized customer service, and ultimate convenience for conducting international business. Ideally located in the heart of central Seoul, THE PLAZA, Seoul, Autograph Collection is optimized for business convenience with free internet service.','4.5','50/684','1825','https://dynamic-media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/1b/6e/91/4f/exterior.jpg?w=400&h=300&s=1','187.000 krw','Seoul','South Korea','Hotel','kr'),
 (17,'Signiel Seoul','300, Olympic-ro, Songpa-gu 76-101F, Lotte World Tower, Seoul 05551 South Korea','Everyone needs a place to lay their weary head. For travelers visiting Seoul, Signiel Seoul is an excellent choice for rest and rejuvenation. Well-known for its charming environment and proximity to great restaurants and attractions, Signiel Seoul makes it easy to enjoy the best of Seoul.    Rooms at Signiel Seoul provide a minibar and air conditioning, and guests can stay connected with free wifi.    In addition, while staying at Signiel Seoul guests have access to a concierge and room service. You can also enjoy a pool and breakfast. Need a place to park? Free parking is available at Signiel Seoul.    Nearby landmarks such as Seoul Seokchon-dong Ancient Tombs (0.7 mi) and World Peace Gate (0.7 mi) make Signiel Seoul a great place to stay when visiting Seoul.    While you’re here, be sure to check out some of the French restaurants, including STAY, Modern Restaurant, Bar 81, and Table 34, all of which are a short distance from Signiel Seoul.    There is no shortage of things to do in the area: explore popular gardens such as Changdeokgung Palace, Namsan Park, and Seoul Children\'s Grand Park.    Whether you’re traveling for business, pleasure or both, Signiel Seoul is sure to make your visit to Seoul one worth remembering.','5.0','6/684','554','https://dynamic-media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/1a/f7/dc/d3/exterior.jpg?w=400&h=300&s=1','304.000 krw','Seoul','South Korea','Hotel','kr'),
