 (159,'Captain Skybar & Restaurant','11th Floor, 58 Hang Gai Hoan Kiem, Hanoi 100000 Vietnam','Captain Sky Bar and Restaurant is centrally located on the side of the Hoan Kiem lake, one of the best spots in Hanoi to drink and enjoy Vietnamese cuisine with amazing panoramic views. Visit us to have a great experience ever.','5.0','31/2345','224','https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-s/18/5d/34/f7/sky-bar.jpg','0','Hanoi','Vietnam','Restaurants','vn'),
 (160,'Tired City Bao Khanh','11A Bao Khanh Alley, Hanoi Vietnam','The very first store of Tired City, a one-of-its-kind company specialized in distributing original and exclusive artworks from Vietnam\'s most prominent young artists in the forms of Apparels, Art Prints, Stationeries...','0','1/385','750','https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-i/0e/a7/45/ac/getlstd-property-photo.jpg','0','Hanoi','Vietnam','Shop','vn'),
 (161,'TiredCity Hang Bong','3 Hang Bong Hang Gai, Hanoi 100000 Vietnam','Located at the corner of Hang Bong and Hang Trong street, the third store of TiredCity system is another humble and cozy space filled with local artworks, a place where tourists can take a small rest from a long walk around the busy Old Quarter, enjoy the spirit of young Vietnamese artists and pick up an adorable gift to bring back home. Welcome to TiredCity.','0','2/385','351','https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-i/17/74/9c/f4/tired-city-hang-bong.jpg','0','Hanoi','Vietnam','Shop','vn'),
 (162,'MasterTan','27 Hang Trong, Hanoi 100000 Vietnam','Proudly presenting the best of Vietnamese ingenuity from all Eras, from tradition to modern. Authentic thousand-year herbal remedies, right next to rustic soap made with Colonial-era know-how and some world-class local pod-to-bean chocolate.','0','3/385','147','https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-i/1b/00/71/d3/hanoi-herbal-gifts-souvenirs.jpg','0','Hanoi','Vietnam','Shop','vn'),
 (163,'Thuy Design House','09 Trang Tien, Hanoi 100000 Vietnam','Thuy Nguyen, the woman of brocade, blends art with fashion to create inspiring designs. Thuy Design House is the brainchild of a strong traditional woman offering a level of femininity and sophistication that is unique in Vietnam. Her background as a successful painter brings into her designs a specialty not many others can offer.','0','4/385','93','https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-f/10/57/58/5a/ao-dai-lua.jpg','0','Hanoi','Vietnam','Shop','vn'),
 (164,'Miranda\'s Jewelry','43 Nguyen Huu Huan, Hoankiem District Next to the most famous Egg Coffee, Giang Cafe, in Old Quarter zone, Hanoi 100000 Vietnam','Miranda\'s - A bit of Vietnamese soul in reminiscence Immersed in the idea of beautiful memories and symbols of the motherland being shaped through the elegant design of sterling silver and rose gold jewelry. We are proud that Miranda\'s is the first brand of Vietnam, by the Vietnamese, to bring the spiritual symbol of the Vietnamese into jewelry designs with internationally standardized production process . A little Vietnam to remember - a little bit to remember, to love carrying the thought about Vietnam - is the common spirit distilled in all the symbols and products that Miranda\'s has, will do research on production and introduce. Our jewelry collections in the theme of Lotus, Conical Hat, Lac bird, Cyclo with their own stories. Located next to Giảng Cafe, the most famous Egg Coffee in VN or in the lounge of Thang Long Water Puppet at Hoan Kiem Lake in Old Quarter area, it’s very easy to find our shops or for more convinient, feel free to call us for delivery in 1hour.','0','5/385','137','https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-f/11/56/5a/c7/miranda-s-jewelry-showroom.jpg','0','Hanoi','Vietnam','Shop','vn'),
 (165,'The Craft House Cathedral - Souvenir & Gift Shop','19 Nha Chung Hoan Kiem, Hanoi 100000 Vietnam','The Craft House is Vietnam\'s first curated retailer of modern craft and design. We are a collective of independent, well established brands based in Vietnam that offer products ranging from handmade stationery, souvenirs to jewlery, leather goods and furnitures. This is our first home in Ha Noi. Hope you guys will enjoy it.','0','6/385','162','https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-i/17/86/1c/68/the-craft-house-cathedral.jpg','0','Hanoi','Vietnam','Shop','vn'),
 (166,'ManGii Custom - Suit and Shoes','78 Hang Gai Hoan Kiem District, Hanoi 100000 Vietnam','ManGii is the one stop shoe store where men can find anything they need for a formal pair of shoes. We provide a unique approach to menswear, where you can design your own shoes, and customize to every single details. All the shoes are made with highest quality leather, with the traditional Blake Stitch or Goodyear method. This mean the shoes sole is sewed together, not glued.','0','7/385','100','https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-f/0e/98/98/c2/every-single-pair-is.jpg','0','Hanoi','Vietnam','Shop','vn'),
 (167,'Collective Memory','12 Nha Chung St, Hoan Kiem District, Hanoi 100000 Vietnam','Founded by a Vietnamese duo of travel writer and photographer, the concept for Collective Memory emerged from a shared enthusiasm for Vietnamese culture. While constantly on the move for assignments, the creators use these opportunities to scour the country for the best products that Vietnam can offer. The concept brings together authentic and high-quality Vietnamese brands under one roof.','0','8/385','173','https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-f/1a/29/49/8b/collective-memory-indoor.jpg','0','Hanoi','Vietnam','Shop','vn'),
 (168,'Cerender Ceramic Shop','11A Trang Thi Street, Hanoi 10000 Vietnam','CERENDER is a brand of hand-made ceramics manufactured in Bat Trang. CERENDER is really outstanding with products: furniture accessories for export like: flower pots, cups, tea sets, plates, table lamps etc., with high-art furniture.','0','9/385','188','https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-i/12/35/c7/7d/getlstd-property-photo.jpg','0','Hanoi','Vietnam','Shop','vn'),
 (169,'54 Traditions Gallery','30 Hang Bun, Hanoi 10000 Vietnam','We focus on two areas: objects and textiles from the ethnic minority groups in the northern mountains of Viet Nam and in the Central Highlands, and also cultural antiques from the Kinh/Viet (the majority group in Viet Nam) and the cultures that preceded them. We have about 1,000 objects on display at a time, and almost all are for sale. All objects are from Viet Nam, are guaranteed to be as described. All are accompanied by a Fact Sheet of at least 1000 words, giving the details on the people who made the object, materials used, purpose, and probable age. We also have inexpensive prints made from antique woodblocks and jewelry, incorporating small antiques and other objects. We work with numerous museums in VN, USA, and elsewhere. Our price range is very broad, with objects under $20 and over $1000.','0','10/385','118','https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-i/0f/d5/67/88/kinh-people-in-the-red.jpg','0','Hanoi','Vietnam','Shop','vn'),
 (170,'Viet Aroma Shop','33A Gia Ngu Hang Bac, Hoan Kiem, Hanoi 110904 Vietnam','Welcome to the shop of Vietnamese and Asian gourmet gifts! Here you can find traditional spices, nuts, dried fruits, candies, coffee beans and teas. There are products from Lao Cai, Thai Nguyen, Dalat, Daklak, Ben Tre provinces and Phu Quoc island. The mission of our shop is collecting delicious high-quality products in our shop and introducing it for our guests.','0','11/385','80','https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-i/13/b9/d3/6d/we-sell-natural-products.jpg','0','Hanoi','Vietnam','Shop','vn'),
