 (172,'Zeds Threads','36 To Ngoc Van Tay Ho, Hanoi 100000 Vietnam','Zeds Threads is a traditional tailor. Each garment is made by a single skilled artisan. Tailoring is our most popular service. We also stock one of the largest collections (in terms of sizing and fit) of men’s clothing for clients who want to buy off the rack. For example, in shirts we have three heights and two fits within each height. Our clothing is predominantly made from 100% natural quality fabrics that are prewashed to minimize shrinkage. Each item is handmade and carefully inspected to make sure it meets our high quality standards. Zeds Threads is based on fair trade principles and a respect for the environment. Our employment policy favours workers from disadvantaged backgrounds. Our goal is to deliver personalised and high quality garments at a fair price, and made under fair working conditions. Prices are very affordable, and provide great value. Please come to our store and try out our clothing for yourself and see our range of quality fabrics. You won\'t be disappointed.','0','15/385','113','https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-f/09/10/7d/0b/zeds-threads.jpg','0','Hanoi','Vietnam','Shop','vn'),
 (173,'Anh Village Silk','36 To Ngoc Van Tay Ho, Hanoi 100000 Vietnam','All our clothing are handmade for men and women. We take and make custom clothing for men, women and children. We sale the following fabrics Silk, Linen, Cotton of various qualities, colors and styles. We can make certain custom orders in as little as 12 hours. We are open to suggests from our customers and make all efforts to ensure their happiness. We also perform custom tailoring.','0','16/358','124','https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-i/15/35/81/b5/texudo.jpg','0','Hanoi','Vietnam','Shop','vn'),
