 (181,'Royal Silk','59 Hang Trong Hoan Kiem, Hanoi 100000 Vietnam','We create tailor-made clothes for men and women in 24hrs We are experts in making Dresses Suits Jumpsuits Runway duplicates Dancewear Everything except underwear xx Choosing us is an experience. The prices for the clothes include a shopping trip to the fabric market and the cost of the fabric. We have clients from all over the world and we keep your measurements on file so we can facilitate international custom orders. Contact us by telephone or WhatsApp with the number on our profile. Thank you in advance for your custom','0','24/385','69','https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-s/0a/29/ae/26/photo4jpg.jpg','0','Hanoi','Vietnam','Shop','vn'),
 (182,'Tohe','14 Nha Chung Hoan Kiem, Hanoi 10000 Vietnam','Tohe is a social enterprise in Vietnam with a clear mission to provide creative learning playgrounds for disadvantaged children. Selected artworks from art classes are redesigned and used as prints for Tohe lifestyle products and 5% of sales will be paid to little author as royalty.','0','25/385','40','https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-f/12/2e/58/5e/100-playful-products.jpg','0','Hanoi','Vietnam','Shop','vn'),
 (183,'Tanmy Design','61 Hang Gai Hoan Kiem District, Hanoi 10000 Vietnam','Tan My Design (TMD) is the most exciting shopping experience in Hanoi, situated at 61 Hang Gai, and occupying over 1000sqm of stunning retail space with an art corner. TMD sits behind a wonderful old facade, and combines the feel of old Hanoi with modern and contemporary architecture and design. TMD features some of Vietnam\'s finest designers-Fashion, Accessories and Homewares as well as TMD own brand. It combines the traditional Tan My values of quality, service and value, with a new and exciting design focus, from the unique design of the shop, spread over 3 floors of spacious and bright shopping, to the modern and relaxing cafe inside.','0','26/385','113','https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-f/0e/cb/4e/31/tmd-embroidery.jpg','0','Hanoi','Vietnam','Shop','vn'),
 (184,'With Love From The Mountains','104 Ma May Street, Hanoi 100000 Vietnam','With Love from the Mountain is a company that deals in exactly that- love from the mountain. Every product that is sold here is %100 handmade by the people from three ethnic groups located in the mountains of northern Vietnam- The Hmong people, the Thai people.','0','27/385','32','https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-i/17/c4/8c/24/with-love-from-the-mountains.jpg','0','Hanoi','Vietnam','Shop','vn'),
 (185,'Heydi Fashion House','12 Chan Cam street Hoan Kiem district, Hanoi 10000 Vietnam','HEYDI BOUTIQUE Tailoring | Designing | Ready to wear Located at No. 12 Chan Cam Street in Old Quarter of Hanoi, run by the top graduate from London Fashion Institute, HEYDI BOUTIQUE offers you unique designed feminine clothing, both ready & tailor made as well as copying on your request. From wedding dresses and bridal gowns for your Big Day to evening wears or daily office lady suites, our professional team will be ready to satisfy your needs. You may choose to take a Fabric market & tailor made design tour in which you enjoy half day/full day tour of Hanoi with our expert fashion designer. During the 5-hour tour, our expert guide/designer Heydi will offer advice, create your own fashion style & carefully design the tailor made products to suit your interests. 24-hour express service is available on your request.','0','28/385','57','https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-s/08/7a/d1/ef/heydi-boutique.jpg','0','Hanoi','Vietnam','Shop','vn'),
 (186,'Chula fashion showroom','43 Nhat Chieu Tay Ho District, Hanoi 110209 Vietnam','In 2004, Laura Fontan and Diego Cortizas arrived in Hanoi Vietnam. The journey for this Spanish couple began soon after they fell in love with the country. They were inspired by “the people, the food, and the colors” and most of all, they were inspired by “all the amazing fabrics and crafts” that surrounded them in their new lives. It was then that they decided to start Chula, a company which has now grown to have a very unique and recognizable image all over Vietnam. The combination of simplicity in shape with their fresh and radical designs served as a starting point and Chula is now a thriving creative company which hopes to continue expanding in the future. We have been steadily growing over the past 12 years and we have become a popular reference in the Vietnamese fashion and art industry. As an expanding company, we have also taken part in many international fashion shows in the United States, Europe, and Asia. As of 2016, there are 5 Chula stores situated around Vietnam, and, with our new and developing systems of websites, we plan to sell to multiple other countries around the world. Chula is also a social company and works with many small local communities in the north of Vietnam. At the moment, it is made up of a skilled community of 60 people, 75% of whom have a physical disability. All our items are made with special care so as to satisfy all customers. We hope you enjoy your Chula experience!','0','29/385','76','https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-s/02/24/79/c0/chula-fashion-showroom.jpg','0','Hanoi','Vietnam','Shop','vn'),
 (187,'Stellar Steakhouse','Keangnam Landmark72 Tower, Pham Hung Street Plot E6, Cau Giay New Urban Area, Me Tri Ward, Nam Tu Liem District, Hanoi 100000 Vietnam','Situated on the 62nd floor of the iconic Landmark72 building, with sweeping night views of Hanoi from above, Stellar Steakhouse is the city\'s most innovative steakhouse, and the only one to dry-age beef in-house, with a unique and remarkable depth of flavour. Premium cuts include the irresistible Mulwarra Premium Black Angus Beef, Black Angus Porterhouse, Wagyu Tenderloin and Kobe Grade A4 Sirloin. Stellar Steakhouse’s resident butchers are on hand to guide you through the extensive menu and to assist with drink pairings. Private dining rooms are available for special events. Stellar Steakhouse also offers exclusive space for wine & cheese tasting, a Whiskey & Sake lounge, as well as Stellar','5.0','36/2345','186','https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-f/1b/3b/15/1c/caption.jpg','0','Hanoi','Vietnam','Restaurants','vn'),
