 (247,'The Shilla Duty Free Seoul','202 Jangchung-dong 2-ga, Jung-gu, Seoul South Korea','The Shilla Duty Free Seoul offers products by world-renowned brands at discounted prices. It is located next to the Shilla Seoul Hotel and provides high-class facilities and services to shoppers.','4.0','27/535','428','https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-i/11/5d/0f/37/the-shilla-duty-free.jpg','0','Seoul','South Korea','Shop','kr'),
