 (319,'Swissotel Merchant Court Singapore','20 Merchant Road Near Clarke Quay MRT station, Singapore 058281 Singapore','Swissotel Merchant Court, Singapore offers the best of both worlds: a central-city location and resort-style ambience. The hotel is ideally located on the banks of the Singapore River, next to Clarke Quay Mass Rapid Transit (MRT) station. Facilities including two award-winning restaurants, one contemporary bar, a resort-style swimming pool, 24-hour Fitness Centre and Purovel Spa & Sport, the region\'s first luxury Swiss spa.','4.5','36/356','6908','https://dynamic-media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/1b/30/79/8a/day-facade-of-swissotel.jpg?w=400&h=300&s=1','189.441 krw','Singapore','Singapore','Hotel','sg'),
 (320,'Park Regis Singapore','23 Merchant Road, Singapore 058268 Singapore','Conveniently located next to Singapore’s most vibrant entertainment hub, Clarke Quay, Boat Quay, Robertson Quay and Chinatown, Park Regis Singapore is within easy access to major tourist attractions as well as the Central Business District. A fully Wi-Fi enabled hotel, featuring 202 modernly designed open-concept guestrooms enhanced with upgraded bedding amenities, onsite restaurant, pillarless meeting room, well-equipped gym and an impressive 25-metre swimming pool with cascading waterfall. The hotel provides all the facilities that you need to complete your stay experience such as the brand new dining restaurant, TASTE by TungLok, self-service laundromat and a Bondi book corner for guests reading pleasure. Park Regis Singapore is an ideal destination to meet, stay and unwind.','4.0','93/356','5135','https://dynamic-media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/08/9b/2c/04/park-regis-singapore.jpg?w=400&h=300&s=1','120.898 krw','Singapore','Singapore','Hotel','sg'),
 (321,'Strand Hotel','25 Bencoolen Street Strand Hotel, Singapore 189619 Singapore','As your “home away from home,” the hotel rooms offer a flat screen TV, a refrigerator, and air conditioning, and getting online is easy, with free wifi available.\r\n\r\nGuests have access to a 24 hour front desk, room service, and a concierge while staying at Strand Hotel Singapore. In addition, Strand Hotel offers free breakfast, which will help make your Singapore trip additionally gratifying. And, as an added convenience, there is parking available to guests.\r\n\r\nFor those interested in checking out popular landmarks while visiting Singapore, Strand Hotel Singapore is located a short distance from Little India (0.5 mi) and Marina Bay Sands Skypark (1.3 mi).\r\n\r\nIf you’re looking for an Italian restaurant, consider a visit to The Lighthouse Restaurant & Rooftop Bar, No Menu, or Beach Road Kitchen, which are all conveniently located a short distance from Strand Hotel Singapore.\r\n\r\nPlus, during your trip, don’t forget to check out some of the popular monuments and statues, such as Merlion Park, Civilian War Memorial, and Statue of Raffles.\r\n\r\nWe’re sure you’ll enjoy your stay at Strand Hotel as ','3.5','162/356','603','https://dynamic-media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/0a/78/b9/dc/the-hotel--v10871696.jpg?w=400&h=300&s=1','107.960 krw','Singapore','Singapore','Hotel','sg'),
