 (369,'Marina Square','6 Raffles Boulevard Marina Square, Singapore 039594, Singapore','Marina Square Shopping Mall is located in the heart of the vibrant shopping, dining, entertainment and cultural hub of Marina Centre, Flanked by 3 world class hotels - Mandarin Oriental Singapore, PARKROYAL COLLECTION Marina Bay and Pan Pacific Singapore, Marina Square is within easy reach of the Marina Bay waterfront and attractions like Gardens By The Bay, the Singapore Flyer, and Esplanade - Theatres on the Bay. Spread over five sprawling levels, the mall houses over 200 specialty shops comprising fashion, food and beverage, leisure and lifestyle concepts. The mall is home to a host of restaurants and coffee joints, including world-class brands. But when you’re in Singapore, the main attraction is the local fare — and at Marina Square, there are plenty of local eats to be sampled in one place.','4.0','129/1012','271','https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-f/04/4c/93/f1/marina-square.jpg','0','Singapore','Singapore','Shop','sg'),
